The formula for each interior angle is:
\[
\frac{(n - 2) \times 180^\circ}{n} = 140^\circ
\]

Solving for \( n \):
\[
140n = 180n - 360 \\
-40n = -360 \\
n = 9
\]

Verification by plugging \( n = 9 \) back into the formula confirms the interior angle is 140°.

