   \[
   \text{Volume of one small hole} = \pi (1)^2 \times 8 = 8\pi \text{ cubic centimeters}
   \]
   \[
   \text{Total volume of two small holes} = 2 \times 8\pi = 16\pi \text{ cubic centimeters}
